msgid ""
"Known limitations, unsupported combinations, and non-goals for the "
"current Klein for Ray alpha release."
msgstr "当前 Klein for Ray alpha 版本的已知限制、不受支持的组合和非目标。"

msgid "Known limitations and non-goals"
msgstr "已知限制和非目标"

msgid ""
"Klein for Ray is alpha software. This page collects the boundaries that "
"are otherwise easy to miss in feature-specific guides. Treat an item as "
"unsupported unless the documentation for the installed release explicitly"
" says otherwise. An unsupported combination can fail during planning, "
"fail when workers start, or run with weaker recovery semantics than the "
"application expects."
msgstr ""
"Klein for Ray 是 alpha "
"软件。本页汇总在特定功能指南中容易忽略的边界。除非所安装版本的文档明确说明支持，否则请将相应项目视为不受支持。不受支持的组合可能在规划期间失败、在"
" worker 启动时失败，或以弱于应用预期的恢复语义运行。"

msgid ""
"The [operator compatibility matrix](operator-compatibility.md) is the "
"concise batch/streaming reference. This page explains the broader product"
" and operational boundaries."
msgstr "[算子兼容性矩阵](operator-compatibility.md)是简明的批处理/流处理参考。本页说明更广泛的产品和运维边界。"

msgid "Platform and compatibility"
msgstr "平台和兼容性"

msgid "Area"
msgstr "领域"

msgid "Current boundary"
msgstr "当前边界"

msgid "Consequence"
msgstr "影响"

msgid "Project status"
msgstr "项目状态"

msgid "Independent alpha project, not maintained or endorsed by Ray"
msgstr "独立的 alpha 项目，不由 Ray 维护，也未获得 Ray 背书"

msgid ""
"Public APIs, checkpoint formats, and behavior can change before 1.0. Pin "
"an exact Klein release."
msgstr "公共 API、检查点格式和行为在 1.0 之前可能发生变化。请固定准确的 Klein 版本。"

msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

msgid "CPython 3.10 through 3.12"
msgstr "CPython 3.10 至 3.12"

msgid "Other Python implementations and versions are not in the tested matrix."
msgstr "其他 Python 实现和版本不在测试矩阵中。"

msgid "Ray"
msgstr "Ray"

msgid "`ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`"
msgstr "`ray[data]>=2.56.1,<2.57`"

msgid ""
"Klein deliberately pins one Ray minor because some Ray Data extension "
"points can change between minors."
msgstr "Klein 有意固定一个 Ray 次版本，因为部分 Ray Data 扩展点可能在次版本之间发生变化。"

msgid "Operating systems"
msgstr "操作系统"

msgid "Linux and macOS are declared by the package"
msgstr "软件包声明支持 Linux 和 macOS"

msgid "Native Windows is not part of the release contract."
msgstr "原生 Windows 不属于发布契约。"

msgid "Language API"
msgstr "语言 API"

msgid "Python only"
msgstr "仅支持 Python"

msgid "There is no Java, Scala, SQL Gateway, or REST job-submission API."
msgstr "没有 Java、Scala、SQL Gateway 或 REST 作业提交 API。"

msgid "Distribution"
msgstr "分发"

msgid "Source checkout and Python wheel"
msgstr "源码检出和 Python wheel"

msgid ""
"Klein does not provide a standalone cluster distribution, container "
"image, Helm chart, or Kubernetes operator. It runs in an existing Ray "
"environment."
msgstr "Klein 不提供独立集群发行版、容器镜像、Helm chart 或 Kubernetes operator。它在现有 Ray 环境中运行。"

msgid ""
"Review [Compatibility](compatibility.md) before changing Python or Ray, "
"and follow [Upgrading](upgrading.md) before changing any component that "
"must read an existing checkpoint."
msgstr ""
"更改 Python 或 Ray "
"前请审查[兼容性](compatibility.md)；更改任何必须读取现有检查点的组件前，请遵循[升级](upgrading.md)。"

msgid "Execution model"
msgstr "执行模型"

msgid ""
"One submitted graph uses one execution mode. Klein does not split a graph"
" into independent batch and streaming regions."
msgstr "一个已提交的图只使用一种执行模式。Klein 不会将一个图拆分为独立的批处理区域和流处理区域。"

msgid ""
"`auto` selects native streaming when any source is unbounded, any graph "
"vertex has no batch lowering, or `udf.ignore-exception=true`; only a "
"fully batch-lowerable, bounded graph with that policy disabled is lowered"
" to Ray Data."
msgstr ""
"任一数据源无界、任一计算图顶点没有批处理下沉实现，或设置 `udf.ignore-exception=true` 时，`auto` "
"会选择原生流处理；只有计算图有界、可完全下沉为批处理，且该策略已禁用时，才会下沉到 Ray Data。"

msgid ""
"A bounded custom `SourceFunction` has no public batch lowering by "
"default, so `auto` selects streaming. Use a Ray Data source when batch "
"execution is required."
msgstr ""
"默认情况下，有界自定义 `SourceFunction` 没有公开的批处理下沉实现，因此 `auto` 会选择流处理。需要批处理执行时，请使用 "
"Ray Data 数据源。"

msgid ""
"Most arbitrary `stream.data` Dataset operations are batch-only. Streaming"
" currently supports the explicitly documented Ray expression forms and "
"native `DataStream` operators."
msgstr ""
"大多数任意 `stream.data` Dataset 操作仅支持批处理。流处理当前支持明确记录的 Ray 表达式形式和原生 "
"`DataStream` 算子。"

msgid ""
"Native streaming is record-oriented with ordered micro-batches. It is not"
" a replacement for Ray Data's batch optimizer, block formats, or "
"autoscaling actor-pool policy."
msgstr "原生流处理以记录为中心，并使用有序微批。它不能替代 Ray Data 的批处理优化器、块格式或自动扩缩 actor 池策略。"

msgid ""
"A graph must have at least one sink before `execute()`. The deprecated "
"interactive mode is retained only for compatibility and is not a "
"production materialization protocol."
msgstr "调用 `execute()` 前，图必须至少有一个 Sink。已弃用的交互模式仅为兼容性而保留，并非生产物化协议。"

msgid ""
"See [Key concepts](key-concepts.md), [Ray Data interoperability](ray-"
"data-interop.md), and [Operator compatibility](operator-compatibility.md)"
" for the selection and lowering rules."
msgstr ""
"有关选择和下沉规则，请参阅[关键概念](key-concepts.md)、[Ray Data 互操作性](ray-data-"
"interop.md)和[算子兼容性](operator-compatibility.md)。"

msgid "SQL and dynamic tables"
msgstr "SQL 和动态表"

msgid ""
"Klein SQL is deliberately smaller than Flink SQL or a general-purpose "
"database. The batch and streaming planners also support different "
"subsets."
msgstr "Klein SQL 有意比 Flink SQL 或通用数据库更精简。批处理和流处理规划器支持的子集也不同。"

msgid ""
"Streaming supports one `SELECT` query block; common table expressions and"
" `UNION ALL` are batch-only."
msgstr "流处理支持一个 `SELECT` 查询块；公共表表达式和 `UNION ALL` 仅支持批处理。"

msgid ""
"Streaming joins are regular inner equality joins. Outer, cross, temporal,"
" interval-SQL, and non-equality joins are not implemented."
msgstr "流式连接仅支持常规内部等值连接。尚未实现外连接、交叉连接、时态连接、区间 SQL 连接和非等值连接。"

msgid ""
"`HAVING`, `SELECT DISTINCT`, recursive common table expressions, SQL "
"window syntax, computed columns, watermarks in DDL, partitions, and "
"catalog-qualified names are not implemented."
msgstr ""
"尚未实现 `HAVING`、`SELECT DISTINCT`、递归公共表表达式、SQL 窗口语法、计算列、DDL 中的水位线、分区以及带 "
"catalog 限定符的名称。"

msgid ""
"Streaming `ORDER BY` requires `LIMIT` and becomes a continuously "
"maintained Top-N. A global Top-N is a single keyed partition."
msgstr "流式 `ORDER BY` 要求同时使用 `LIMIT`，并转化为持续维护的 Top-N。全局 Top-N 是单个键控分区。"

msgid ""
"Regular joins, non-windowed aggregations, and Top-N can grow without "
"bound unless state TTL is configured. TTL can make later results "
"incomplete."
msgstr "除非配置状态 TTL，否则常规连接、非窗口聚合和 Top-N 可能无限增长。TTL 可能使后续结果不完整。"

msgid ""
"Updating queries emit changelog rows. Ordinary append sinks do not "
"automatically materialize update-before, update-after, or delete records."
msgstr ""
"更新查询会发出 changelog 行。普通追加 Sink 不会自动物化 update-before、update-after 或 delete "
"记录。"

msgid ""
"SQLGlot parses the query, but Klein owns validation and execution. "
"Installing another SQLGlot version or a database engine does not add SQL "
"features."
msgstr "SQLGlot 负责解析查询，但验证和执行由 Klein 负责。安装其他 SQLGlot 版本或数据库引擎不会增加 SQL 功能。"

msgid ""
"The authoritative query matrix and expression rules are in [SQL and Table"
" APIs](sql.md#how-does-sql-execute)."
msgstr "权威的查询矩阵和表达式规则见 [SQL 和 Table API](sql.md#how-does-sql-execute)。"

msgid "State, checkpoints, and recovery"
msgstr "状态、检查点和恢复"

msgid ""
"Klein checkpoints provide a consistent recovery boundary for supported "
"native streaming sources, managed state, timers, and prepared "
"transactional sink output. They do not make every external effect exactly"
" once."
msgstr ""
"Klein 检查点为受支持的原生流式数据源、托管状态、定时器和已预备的事务型 Sink "
"输出提供一致的恢复边界。它们不会让每个外部副作用都变为精确一次。"

msgid "Boundary"
msgstr "边界"

msgid "Current behavior"
msgstr "当前行为"

msgid "General delivery"
msgstr "一般交付保证"

msgid ""
"At least once. Non-transactional sinks can observe duplicates after "
"replay."
msgstr "至少一次。重放后，非事务型 Sink 可能观察到重复项。"

msgid "State backends"
msgstr "状态后端"

msgid ""
"In-memory and optional local RocksDB working state. Durable recovery "
"still requires checkpoint storage."
msgstr "内存和可选的本地 RocksDB 工作状态。持久恢复仍需要检查点存储。"

msgid "Durable checkpoint stores"
msgstr "持久检查点存储"

msgid ""
"Local/file, Amazon S3-compatible, and Google Cloud Storage URIs through "
"the documented filesystem adapter."
msgstr "通过文档所述的文件系统适配器支持本地/file、Amazon S3 兼容和 Google Cloud Storage URI。"

msgid "Savepoints"
msgstr "Savepoint"

msgid ""
"`execution.savepoint.path` can restore a recorded completed checkpoint, "
"but there is no command that creates a separately managed Flink-style "
"savepoint."
msgstr ""
"`execution.savepoint.path` 可以恢复已记录的已完成检查点，但没有用于创建单独管理的 Flink 风格 savepoint"
" 的命令。"

msgid "JobManager loss"
msgstr "JobManager 丢失"

msgid ""
"Losing the JobManager currently requires resubmitting the same job "
"definition from a durable completed checkpoint."
msgstr "JobManager 丢失后，当前需要从持久的已完成检查点重新提交相同的作业定义。"

msgid "Whole-cluster loss"
msgstr "整个集群丢失"

msgid ""
"Recovery is a new submission; Klein does not recreate a Ray cluster or "
"resubmit the application."
msgstr "恢复需要重新提交；Klein 不会重新创建 Ray 集群或重新提交应用。"

msgid "State schema migration"
msgstr "状态模式迁移"

msgid "No automatic migration framework is promised for alpha checkpoints."
msgstr "不承诺为 alpha 检查点提供自动迁移框架。"

msgid "Serialization"
msgstr "序列化"

msgid ""
"Python objects, functions, keys, and state must be serializable and "
"should be treated as trusted data."
msgstr "Python 对象、函数、键和状态必须可序列化，并且应视为受信任数据。"

msgid "Maximum parallelism"
msgstr "最大并行度"

msgid ""
"`state.keyed.max-parallelism` fixes the key-group space and cannot change"
" when an existing checkpoint must remain restorable."
msgstr "`state.keyed.max-parallelism` 固定键组空间；当现有检查点必须保持可恢复时，不能更改该值。"

msgid ""
"Checkpoint metadata only covers components in its checkpoint domain. "
"Broker acknowledgements, database commits, remote API calls, and "
"arbitrary UDF side effects remain external consistency boundaries. Read "
"[Delivery semantics](delivery-semantics.md), [Checkpoint storage"
"](checkpoint-storage.md), and [Restore and rescale](checkpoint-"
"recovery.md) together before defining an RPO or RTO."
msgstr ""
"检查点元数据只覆盖其检查点域中的组件。broker 确认、数据库提交、远程 API 调用和任意 UDF 副作用仍属于外部一致性边界。定义 RPO "
"或 RTO 前，请结合阅读[交付语义](delivery-semantics.md)、[检查点存储](checkpoint-"
"storage.md)和[恢复与扩缩](checkpoint-recovery.md)。"

msgid "Scaling and scheduling"
msgstr "扩缩和调度"

msgid ""
"Klein separates Ray Data worker autoscaling, native streaming operator "
"parallelism, and Ray cluster node autoscaling."
msgstr "Klein 将 Ray Data worker 自动扩缩、原生流处理算子并行度和 Ray 集群节点自动扩缩区分开来。"

msgid ""
"There is no built-in metric-driven controller for streaming operator "
"parallelism. The Dashboard and state API perform explicit changes."
msgstr "没有用于流处理算子并行度的内置指标驱动控制器。Dashboard 和状态 API 执行显式变更。"

msgid ""
"Live local rescaling does not support source operators, collecting sinks,"
" or transactional sinks."
msgstr "在线局部扩缩不支持数据源算子、收集型 Sink 或事务型 Sink。"

msgid ""
"Only one live operator rescale can run at a time, and another change must"
" wait for the stabilization checkpoint."
msgstr "一次只能执行一个在线算子扩缩；下一次变更必须等待稳定检查点。"

msgid ""
"Scale-out actors added after initial placement use native Ray placement. "
"Existing placement-group bundles are not resized, and scale-in does not "
"guarantee that Ray can release a node."
msgstr "初始放置后新增的扩容 actor 使用原生 Ray 放置。现有放置组 bundle 不会调整大小，缩容也不保证 Ray 能释放节点。"

msgid ""
"Operator chaining changes the physical scaling unit. A transform chained "
"to an unsupported source cannot be resized independently."
msgstr "算子链会改变物理扩缩单元。与不受支持的数据源链接的转换无法独立调整大小。"

msgid ""
"Hot keys, single global aggregations, external rate limits, and serial "
"sinks do not become parallel merely because another operator is enlarged."
msgstr "热点键、单一全局聚合、外部速率限制和串行 Sink 不会仅因为扩大另一个算子就变为并行。"

msgid ""
"Ray's cluster autoscaler can satisfy resource demand but does not decide "
"Klein operator parallelism."
msgstr "Ray 集群自动扩缩器可以满足资源需求，但不会决定 Klein 算子并行度。"

msgid ""
"See [Autoscaling and live operator rescaling](operator-rescaling.md) for "
"the admission rules, rollback boundary, and stabilization fence."
msgstr "有关准入规则、回滚边界和稳定栅栏，请参阅[自动扩缩与在线算子扩缩](operator-rescaling.md)。"

msgid "Connector guarantees"
msgstr "连接器保证"

msgid "Connector behavior is not uniform:"
msgstr "连接器行为并不统一："

msgid ""
"Streaming Kafka output is at least once and does not use Kafka "
"transactions."
msgstr "流式 Kafka 输出为至少一次，不使用 Kafka 事务。"

msgid ""
"RocketMQ progress is owned by its consumer group and can advance ahead of"
" a durable Klein checkpoint. A full rollback can therefore lose "
"acknowledged messages relative to that checkpoint."
msgstr "RocketMQ 进度由其消费者组管理，可能领先于持久 Klein 检查点。因此，相对于该检查点，完全回滚可能丢失已确认的消息。"

msgid ""
"Streaming Iceberg supports append only. Overwrite and upsert remain "
"batch-only."
msgstr "流式 Iceberg 仅支持追加。覆盖和 upsert 仍仅支持批处理。"

msgid ""
"Filesystem and Iceberg append output is checkpoint-transactional, but "
"readers and catalog retention still need to follow their documented "
"commit protocol."
msgstr "文件系统和 Iceberg 追加输出具有检查点事务性，但读取方和 catalog 保留仍需遵循各自记录的提交协议。"

msgid ""
"SQL, Redis, console, and ordinary custom sinks are not globally "
"transactional."
msgstr "SQL、Redis、控制台和普通自定义 Sink 不具备全局事务性。"

msgid ""
"A custom `SourceFunction` or `SinkFunction` defines part of the recovery "
"contract. Klein cannot infer whether its external side effects are "
"idempotent."
msgstr "自定义 `SourceFunction` 或 `SinkFunction` 定义恢复契约的一部分。Klein 无法推断其外部副作用是否幂等。"

msgid ""
"Optional connector libraries and native dependencies must be present on "
"every worker that may execute the connector."
msgstr "每个可能执行连接器的 worker 都必须安装可选连接器库和原生依赖。"

msgid ""
"Use the [connector capability matrix](connectors/index.md#capability-"
"matrix) and the connector's own delivery section before combining a "
"source and sink."
msgstr ""
"组合数据源与 Sink 前，请查阅[连接器能力矩阵](connectors/index.md#capability-"
"matrix)以及连接器自身的交付章节。"

msgid "Operations and security"
msgstr "运维和安全"

msgid ""
"The bundled Dashboard has no authentication or TLS. It binds to loopback "
"by default and refuses a non-loopback listener unless the operator "
"explicitly accepts the risk."
msgstr "内置 Dashboard 没有身份验证或 TLS。它默认绑定回环地址；除非运维方明确接受风险，否则会拒绝监听非回环地址。"

msgid ""
"The Dashboard control endpoint can rescale supported operators. The CLI "
"and Python state API can also cancel jobs. Protect every control path "
"with the Ray and network boundary documented in the security guide."
msgstr ""
"Dashboard 控制端点可以对受支持的算子进行扩缩容。CLI 和 Python 状态 API 还可以取消作业。请使用安全指南中说明的 Ray "
"与网络边界保护每条控制路径。"

msgid ""
"The detached state actor keeps a bounded in-memory job history. It is not"
" an audit log, durable metric store, or source of checkpoint truth."
msgstr "分离的状态 actor 保留有界的内存作业历史。它不是审计日志、持久指标存储或检查点事实来源。"

msgid ""
"Klein relies on Ray and the deployment platform for cluster "
"authentication, network isolation, process isolation, secret delivery, "
"and multi-tenant policy."
msgstr "Klein 依赖 Ray 和部署平台提供集群身份验证、网络隔离、进程隔离、密钥交付和多租户策略。"

msgid ""
"User-defined functions execute arbitrary Python with the worker process's"
" identity and credentials. Klein does not sandbox them."
msgstr "用户定义函数以 worker 进程的身份和凭据执行任意 Python。Klein 不会对其进行沙箱隔离。"

msgid ""
"Checkpoint and application artifacts must come from a trusted source. "
"Loading Python-serialized state from an untrusted location is unsafe."
msgstr "检查点和应用构件必须来自受信任来源。从不受信任的位置加载 Python 序列化状态是不安全的。"

msgid ""
"Configuration redaction is defense in depth, not a secret store. Do not "
"put credentials in logs, record values, metric labels, job names, or "
"operator names."
msgstr "配置脱敏属于纵深防御，并非密钥存储。不要将凭据放入日志、记录值、指标标签、作业名或算子名。"

msgid ""
"Read [Security and trust boundaries](security.md) before exposing any Ray"
" or Klein endpoint."
msgstr "暴露任何 Ray 或 Klein 端点前，请阅读[安全和信任边界](security.md)。"

msgid "Explicit non-goals"
msgstr "明确的非目标"

msgid "The current standalone project does not aim to:"
msgstr "当前独立项目并不旨在："

msgid ""
"replace Ray Core, Ray Data, Ray Jobs, Ray Serve, KubeRay, or the Ray "
"autoscaler;"
msgstr "替代 Ray Core、Ray Data、Ray Jobs、Ray Serve、KubeRay 或 Ray 自动扩缩器；"

msgid ""
"reproduce every Flink API, connector, SQL feature, deployment target, or "
"exactly-once protocol;"
msgstr "复现每个 Flink API、连接器、SQL 功能、部署目标或精确一次协议；"

msgid "provide a public multi-tenant control plane or hosted service;"
msgstr "提供公共多租户控制平面或托管服务；"

msgid "infer external-system correctness from a Python connector implementation;"
msgstr "根据 Python 连接器实现推断外部系统正确性；"

msgid "guarantee checkpoint compatibility across arbitrary alpha revisions; or"
msgstr "保证任意 alpha 修订版之间的检查点兼容性；或"

msgid ""
"make internal modules under `ray.klein._internal` or `ray.klein.runtime` "
"stable application APIs."
msgstr "将 `ray.klein._internal` 或 `ray.klein.runtime` 下的内部模块变为稳定的应用 API。"

msgid ""
"If an application depends on a missing capability, open an issue before "
"building around an internal module. Include the execution mode, recovery "
"requirement, connector pair, state size, and expected compatibility "
"window."
msgstr "如果应用依赖缺失的能力，请在围绕内部模块构建之前提交 issue。请包含执行模式、恢复要求、连接器组合、状态大小和预期兼容窗口。"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "The Dashboard control endpoint can "
#~ "cancel jobs and rescale supported "
#~ "operators. Put it behind an "
#~ "authenticated proxy if it is exposed "
#~ "at all."
#~ msgstr "Dashboard 控制端点可以取消作业并扩缩受支持的算子。如果需要暴露该端点，请将其置于经过身份验证的代理之后。"
